---
// CustomerSegments.astro
---
<section class="section" id="customers">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">🏦 Who It's For</div>
      <h2>Fast-forward your AI deployments.</h2>
      <p>We focus on Financial Institutions to help them accelerate their AI deployments by taking care of their compliance needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="segments-grid">
      <!-- Segment 1: Beachhead -->
      <div class="segment-card card segment--primary" id="segment-banks">
        <div class="segment-badge">
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">⭐ Primary Market</span>
          <span class="segment-years">Years 1–3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="segment-header">
          <div class="segment-icon">🏦</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Banks ($50B – $500B assets)</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="segment-why" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem;">Because you are smaller and don't have a 10,000 member engineering team, you rely on AI to scale. But right now, your risk teams are blocking production because manual incident reconstruction takes days. We remove that governance paralysis so you can deploy faster.</p>


      </div>

      <!-- Segment 2: FinTechs -->
      <div class="segment-card card segment--secondary" id="segment-fintechs">
        <div class="segment-badge">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">Secondary Market</span>
          <span class="segment-years">Year 2+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="segment-header">
          <div class="segment-icon">🚀</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Regulated FinTechs</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="segment-why" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem;">You are unlocking next-generation financial experiences. But regulatory speed limits and audit exposure are threatening to halt your AI deployments. We ensure your infrastructure scales safely with out-of-the-box evidence generation.</p>


  </div>
</section>

<style>
.segments-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.segment-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.segment--primary {
  border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, rgba(0,212,255,0.02) 100%);
}

.segment-badge {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.segment-years {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
}

.segment-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.segment-icon { font-size: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.segment-header h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
.segment-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.segment-jurisdictions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

.segment-why { font-size: 0.9rem; }
.segment-why strong { color: var(--color-cyan); }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .segments-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
